.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Scratch
**/results.txt
**/dbg.txt
**/test-out.txt

# Local Claude Code harness settings (machine-specific)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/*.lock
broker/.uitmp/
**/cron-jobs.json
